      <title>AdGuard 广告拦截器</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/01/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/01/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>AdGuard 是快速的、小内存的广告拦截扩展，可高效拦截所有网页上的各种广告！选择所需的 AdGuard 浏览器扩展，您可进行无广告、快速、安全的浏览。</strong></p><p>1.打开AdGuard广告拦截器扩展安装界面（<a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/adguard-%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/pdffkfellgipmhklpdmokmckkkfcopbh">传送门</a>）</p><p>2.点击获取进行安装</p><details class="toggle"><summary class="toggle-button" style>查看图片</summary><div class="toggle-content"><p><img src="/2022/07/01/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A81.png"></p></div></details><p>3.在弹出的配置 AdGuard 扩展页面中打开前四个设置</p><details class="toggle"><summary class="toggle-button" style>查看图片</summary><div class="toggle-content"><p><img src="/2022/07/01/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A82.png"></p></div></details>]]></content>
      
      
